property.name: Text
property.value: This is the way up the mountain — I call it Cold Peak. Dangers await. Nay, they lurk. Sally forth with bravery, dear traveler, and you shalll assuredly prevail! —J.M.

property.name: Text
property.value: The road splits ahead, traveler. The upper path will take you to the summit of the mountain, while the lower path will bring you through a cave system. At the end of each there's a treasure. I bested both paths, long ago, when I was a youth. I never forgot the experience, so I’ve returned now, near my end, to see both beauties again. These signs will be my legacy! Ha HA! —J.M.

property.name: Text
property.value: Traveler! This is the path down through the caves — what I call the Heat Archipelago. (I was of course the first to name it.) Take heart! Your journey is about to begin! — J.M.
